{
  "stem": "12674.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we-- we could-- we could have milk in the house that we could buy, if we got some that didn't go bad.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because there were no refrigerators.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were no cooking stove.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everything was makeshift.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had-- the closets we had where we hung out clothes were out of some [NON-ENGLISH], the book closets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had to leave all our furniture behind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everything was makeshift.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No bed-- no-- nothing fit with one another and no silverware, no china, nothing-- five plates.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It-- it was a mess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But this-- this isn't what count.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What counts is whether you survive and that you live from day to day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And nobody beats you, and nobody injures you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They work you to death, but we were used to that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were living in hell, and those-- those were the rules that-- that-- I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I did stupid things because I'm stupid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We-- we-- well, I was young and-- and ignorant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I remember what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I figured it out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "What we did is we printed some things, some anti-something, and-- and we-- and-- and I had the idea of going to an el station and putting it on a-- on a-- on one of the posts, you know, there on those things.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They had like these marble things, and I put it on the top there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and-- and-- and-- and-- and-- and-- and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when the train came, the wind pushed the leaves away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were long gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "If anybody would have seen-- and then they were flying all over, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They were flying, and they came down to the street, you know, like an elevator train like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And of course, they found out where they were coming from.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
